oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kingston street scene
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Kingston taken shortly after the Civil War. There are people standing in a line across the dirt road. There are also people standing on a porch to the left, and on a balcony on the right.
